com.google.gwt.uibinder.client

Annotation Type UiFactory


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface UiFactory
    Marks a method that may be called as an alternative to a GWT.create call in a UiBinder template. The parameter names of the method are treated as required xml element attribute values.

    It is an error to apply this annotation to more than one method of a given return type.
